==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Jury mast
<hw>Ju"ry mast</hw>. <sd>(a)</sd> <def>A temporary mast, in place of one
that has been carried away, or broken.</def> <sd>(b)</sd>
<fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>An apparatus to support the trunk and head in
spinal disease.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Jury-rig</ent>⟦br⟧
